<item chapterid="598058" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1931" articlename="绝世村痞" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521622761" lastupdate="1521622761" chaptername="第0章心的历程" chapterorder="245" size="6111" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    一会儿，等罗局走了之后，咱们杨易杨公子有些呆呆的站立在会客室的中央……

