<item chapterid="598101" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1931" articlename="绝世村痞" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521622761" lastupdate="1521622761" chaptername="第0章能文能武" chapterorder="288" size="6199" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    不一会儿，杨易和曾志全等人也就打车来到了市委大院的门前。

