<item chapterid="598116" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1931" articlename="绝世村痞" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521622761" lastupdate="1521622761" chaptername="第0章感受一把权力" chapterorder="303" size="6191" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    待一会儿杨易来到了曾书记的办公室门前时，也就抬手敲了敲门：“咚咚咚……”

