<item chapterid="598132" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1931" articlename="绝世村痞" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521622761" lastupdate="1521622761" chaptername="第0章女孩就是蛮不讲理" chapterorder="319" size="6098" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    又听得杨易那么的说着，楚焉琪又是两颊搴斓陌琢怂一眼，然后嘴巴一撅，哼了一声，便气呼呼的扭身走了。

