<item chapterid="598313" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1931" articlename="绝世村痞" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521622761" lastupdate="1521622761" chaptername="第0章很坑爹" chapterorder="500" size="6154" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    之后，当咱们杨局在小廊街找着了那个武江市同乡会联络处时，心里登时那个失落呀，不知道咋形容才是好？

