<item chapterid="598382" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1931" articlename="绝世村痞" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521622761" lastupdate="1521622761" chaptername="第0章遭报应" chapterorder="569" size="6108" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    这会儿，关于金觇金公子那不被人同情的惨案一事，现正式直接由县公安局介入调查。

