<item chapterid="598385" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1931" articlename="绝世村痞" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521622761" lastupdate="1521622761" chaptername="第0章也许是报应" chapterorder="572" size="6124" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    这天上午，关于金觇一案，三乡县县公安局宣布已经告破，两名主犯已经被抓获。

