<item chapterid="598389" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1931" articlename="绝世村痞" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521622761" lastupdate="1521622761" chaptername="第0章谈话" chapterorder="576" size="6126" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    由于这交谈看似和谐、却又没啥实质的共同的话题，所以余建城也是感觉有些尴尬，貌似交谈不下去了，无奈之下，余建城也只好逍Φ溃骸澳牵杨县长，你就……忙你的吧？”

