<item chapterid="598393" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1931" articlename="绝世村痞" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521622761" lastupdate="1521622761" chaptername="第0章问责" chapterorder="580" size="6081" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    一会儿，当余建城来到第三会议室门前时，心里不由得愈加的忐忑了起来……

