<item chapterid="598420" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1931" articlename="绝世村痞" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521622761" lastupdate="1521622761" chaptername="第0章韦芳忽听来电" chapterorder="607" size="6108" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    这天上午的会议结束后，咱们杨易杨县长他还在想着他与紫晴的那些事……

